# 🐳 STEP 1 — Start Jenkins in Docker

## 📍 Where to do this:

👉 Open **Terminal (PowerShell / VS Code terminal)**

---

## ▶ Run these commands ONE BY ONE

### 1️⃣ Create volume

```bash
docker volume create jenkins-data
```

---

### 2️⃣ Run Jenkins container

```bash
docker run -d ^
  --name jenkins ^
  -p 8081:8080 -p 50001:50000 ^
  -v jenkins-data:/var/jenkins_home ^
  -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock ^
  jenkins/jenkins:lts
```

👉 I used **8081 (not 8080)** to avoid conflict

---

### 3️⃣ Get admin password

```bash
docker exec jenkins cat /var/jenkins_home/secrets/initialAdminPassword
```

👉 Copy the long password

---

